Package org.javalite.activeweb.proxy

Class PrintWriterProxy

java.lang.Object
java.io.Writer
java.io.PrintWriter
org.javalite.activeweb.proxy.PrintWriterProxy
All Implemented Interfaces:
Closeable, Flushable, Appendable, AutoCloseable
public class PrintWriterProxy extends PrintWriter
This class exists to catch a case when a client disconnected from the server during a long download or streaming.
